{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 51,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الذَّارِيَاتِ",
    "englishName": "Adh-Dhaariyat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Winnowing Winds",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 60,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4676,
        "text": "以散布的风、",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4677,
        "text": "载着含雨的云、",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4678,
        "text": "自由飘流[的船舶]、",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4679,
        "text": "奉[安拉之]命分配[给养、雨水和其他恩赐物]者[天使]发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4680,
        "text": "凡许诺你们的[后世的复活，善奖恶罚等]都是真实的，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4681,
        "text": "审判确是要发生的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4682,
        "text": "以有轨道的天体发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4683,
        "text": "你们[对穆圣和《古兰经》]确是各执一词的。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4684,
        "text": "[根据安拉的判决和前定]背离[穆圣和《古兰经》]者背离了。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4685,
        "text": "该遭谴责的说谎者！",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4686,
        "text": "他们[说谎者]常沉溺于愚昧的说谎中。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4687,
        "text": "他们常问：“审判日在什么时候？”",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4688,
        "text": "那是他们在火狱上受刑之日。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4689,
        "text": "[有话声对他们说]：“你们尝试你们[被烧灼]的刑罚吧！这就是你们[生前]要求早日实现的刑罚。”",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4690,
        "text": "敬畏者必将住在乐园和泉水旁，",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4691,
        "text": "接受他们的主赐予他们的，因为他们此前确是行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4692,
        "text": "夜里，他们经常少睡[注][用大部分时间祈求安拉，如礼拜]；",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4693,
        "text": "黎明前，他们就[向安拉]求饶。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4694,
        "text": "在他们的财产中，乞求者和贫民均有份额。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4695,
        "text": "对笃信[安拉]者，大地上有许多迹象，",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4696,
        "text": "你们自身中也有许多迹象。难道你们没有观察吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4697,
        "text": "天上有你们的给养和你们所被许诺的一切。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4698,
        "text": "以天地的主[安拉]发誓！这[你们所被许诺的]确是真实的，犹如你们讲实话一样[真实]。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4699,
        "text": "伊布拉欣的贵客[吉布里勒天使和另外两位天使]的故事到达你[穆圣]了吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4700,
        "text": "当时，他们[三位天使]进去见他[伊布拉欣]。他们说：“祝你平安！”他说：“[也]祝你们平安！”[他还说]：“你们是我不认识的陌生人。”",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4701,
        "text": "然后，他悄悄到他的家人那里，接着便拿来一只烤牛犊[据说伊布拉欣圣人的财产大部分是牛]。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4702,
        "text": "他把那牛犊放到他们面前，他说：“你们不会吃吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4703,
        "text": "[因为他们不吃烤牛犊]他感到有点害怕他们。他们说：“你不要害怕。”他们以一个[对安拉及其宗教]聪敏的儿子向他报喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4704,
        "text": "他的妻子叫嚷着走来，打着她的脸说：“我是一个不能生育的老妇了。”",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4705,
        "text": "他们说：“你的主[安拉]是这样说的。他[安拉]确是最睿智的，全知的。”",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4706,
        "text": "他[伊布拉欣]说：“使者们[天使]啊！你们的使命是什么？”",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4707,
        "text": "他们说：“我们奉命去惩治一群犯罪的民众，",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4708,
        "text": "我们将降下烧过的粘土般的石块惩治他们，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4709,
        "text": "[那些石块]在你的主那里是为惩罚过分者[超越法度者]而打上烙印的。”",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4710,
        "text": "我救出了城中的信士，",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4711,
        "text": "但我在城中只发现一家穆斯林[鲁特圣人和他的两个女儿]。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4712,
        "text": "我在那里给畏惧痛苦的刑罚者留下了一种迹象[死海]。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4713,
        "text": "在穆萨的故事中[也有一种迹象]。当时，我派他带着一种明证去见法老。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4714,
        "text": "但他[法老]依仗他的权势[军队]背弃他[穆萨]。他[法老]说：“[你是]一个魔术师或疯子。”",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4715,
        "text": "所以，我惩治了他和他的军队，我把他们扔进大海中[淹死]，因为他[法老]是应受谴责的。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4716,
        "text": "在阿德人的故事中[也有一种迹象]。当时，我派毁灭性的狂风惩罚他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4717,
        "text": "凡是狂风经过之处，全部毁为碎片。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4718,
        "text": "在萨姆德人的故事中[也有一种迹象]。当时，有话声对他们说：“你们暂时享受吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4719,
        "text": "但他们违抗他们的主的命令，所以，霹雳声在他们亲眼目睹下袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4720,
        "text": "因此，他们站不起来，也不能自救。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4721,
        "text": "在他们之前，[我曾毁灭了]努哈的族人。他们是悖逆的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4722,
        "text": "我以我的权力建造了天，我确是万物的创造者。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4723,
        "text": "我展开了大地。我是多么卓越的展开者啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4724,
        "text": "我把每种物都造成两性的，以便你们思考[安拉的恩惠]。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4725,
        "text": "[你说]：“你们赶快逃归安拉吧[从将遭安拉的惩罚逃向获取安拉的宽恕和慈悯——伊斯兰教]！我确是他派遣给你们的坦率的警告者[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4726,
        "text": "你们不要既拜安拉，又拜其他神灵，我确是他派遣给你们的坦率的警告者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4727,
        "text": "他们的前人也是这样，每当有使者来临他们，他们必[对他]说：“[你是]一个魔术师或疯子。”",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4728,
        "text": "难道他们[前人]以此嘱咐这些人[古莱什的异教徒]吗？其实，他们是叛逆的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4729,
        "text": "你[穆圣]当避开他们[古莱什的异教徒]，你是不受责备的[因为你已向他们传达了安拉的启示]。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4730,
        "text": "你当[以《古兰经》]教诲[人类]，因为教诲对信士们确是有益的。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4731,
        "text": "我[安拉]创造精灵和人类，目的是让他们崇拜我。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4732,
        "text": "我不要他们的任何供养，我不要他们供我饮食。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4733,
        "text": "安拉确是[万物]最好的供给者，确是最有权力的，确是最强大的[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4734,
        "text": "不义者必将遭受他们昔日的伙伴们所遭受的刑罚，所以，叫他们不要催促我早日实现刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4735,
        "text": "不信仰者被警告的日子来临时，他们[不信仰者]将遭严惩真活该！",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
